nodes.text: Star Wars: Doctor Aphra: Fortune and Fate

Star Wars: Doctor Aphra: Fortune and Fate is the first story arc of Marvel Comics' ongoing 2020 series Star Wars: Doctor Aphra. The arc comprises the first five issues of the series, and was written by Alyssa Wong, with art by Marika Cresta.
